  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a standard action, you can assume the form of a Small or Medium animal, as @Compendium[pf1.spells.tjdfluulncmqacc3]{Beast Shape I}.</p>\n<p>At 9th level, you can assume the form of a Tiny or Large animal, as @Compendium[pf1.spells.774kmgcb7ygviht0]{Beast Shape II}.</p>\n<p>At 11th level, you can assume the form of a Diminutive or Huge animal or a Small or Medium magical beast, as @Compendium[pf1.spells.w88ddxpu89qcr5c0]{Beast Shape III}.</p>\n<p>At 13th level, you can assume the form of a Tiny or Large magical beast, as @Compendium[pf1.spells.br37848gchetel0q]{Beast Shape IV}.</p>\n<p>You can use this ability once per day, but the duration is 1 hour/level.</p>\n<p>You must be at least 7th level to select this revelation.</p>"
